<view class="page">
  <view class="page-head"><text class="eyebrow">只读小技能</text><text class="hero-title">出走小技能</text><text class="subtext">这些不是指令，只是一些可以复制走的小提醒。</text></view>
  <view wx:for="{{skills}}" wx:key="title" class="paper-card"><text class="section-title">{{item.title}}</text><text class="body-text">{{item.content}}</text><button class="sticker-button green" data-index="{{index}}" bindtap="copySkill">复制这条</button></view>
</view>
